node.text:
The last 9 years living at my Bel Air estate have been wonderful. I have so many amazing memories that I will cherish forever. From the diamond parties to the fund raising and numerous events, I have been able to showcase this beautiful home to many socialites, celebrities, and politicians… The who is who in Los Angeles and Hollywood.  I am now nearing completion of my next dream home in the bird streets and will need to detach emotionally from my beautiful Bel Air property. Who will be the next owner?
.
#LifeWithPascal #belair #losangeles #beverlyhills #hollywood #realestate #california #la

Leveraging the eminent artistry and skills of Mouawad craftsmen, the Mouawad Dragon Suite is as unforgettable as the diamond that first inspired it.
